 "remarks": "Beautifully updated with main level primary suite and abundant additional living space for family and guests in this move-in ready townhouse. You will love the soaring ceilings, the open and very flexible floor plan and natural light that fills this home throughout the day. Enjoy coffee or dinner al fresco on your dedicated private patio - so rarely found in a condominium community. Almost fully revamped with high quality materials and a simple but stunning palette that will appeal to every taste and decor. One of the largest 2 bedroom 2.5 bath models, this unit includes an upper level open loft or office plus a finished lower level for your home theater or gym and extensive storage in the unfinished area. Every detail has been considered for comfort and peace of mind, including a generator and hard-wired security system. Harvest Commons is a vibrant and well managed community with pool, pool house and tennis courts. Ideally located close to shopping, dining, Metro North and our beaches. No need to downsize - this is an opportunity to &quot;right size&quot; and enjoy all the advantages of a home, without the headaches.",
